<h4 id="2-rip-routing-information-protocol">2. RIP (Routing Information Protocol)</h4>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: left">кµ¬л¶„</th>
      <th style="text-align: left">л‚ґмљ©</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">к°њл…ђ</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">RFC 1058м—ђ м •мќлђм–ґ мћ€кі  лЊЂн‘њм Ѓмќё к±°л¦¬ лІЎн„° лќјмљ°нЊ… н”„лЎњн† мЅњ</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">лЏ™мћ‘ м›ђл¦¬</td>
